WEBVTT


00:00:00.840 --> 00:00:02.391
No Bible read today?

00:00:02.392 --> 00:00:04.481
no problem we read them together

00:00:04.840 --> 00:00:06.760
this Bible passage helps me again and again

00:00:07.120 --> 00:00:09.000
when worries take me completely

00:00:09.280 --> 00:00:13.720
when fears block my view and make it difficult to trust God

00:00:14.320 --> 00:00:17.800
maybe this Bible passage will help you too you must know it

00:00:18.200 --> 00:00:20.040
no matter where you are in the car in bed

00:00:20.600 --> 00:00:21.483
in the train, 

00:00:21.483 --> 00:00:23.880
ey listen to it and let it go over you

00:00:24.280 --> 00:00:26.728
"A song from David"

00:00:26.729 --> 00:00:27.761
October 23

00:00:28.760 --> 00:00:30.440
the Lord is my shepherd

00:00:31.280 --> 00:00:33.240
nothing will be missing

00:00:33.960 --> 00:00:39.680
he feeds me in lushs and leads me to fresh springs

00:00:40.920 --> 00:00:42.320
he gives me new strength

00:00:43.160 --> 00:00:49.840
he guides me in safe ways and makes his name so that all honor

00:00:50.760 --> 00:00:54.280
and even when going through dark valleys

00:00:55.200 --> 00:00:56.520
I fear no misfortune

00:00:57.440 --> 00:00:59.560
For you Lord are with me

00:01:00.240 --> 00:01:04.120
your shepherd's crook gives me protection and comfort

00:01:04.879 --> 00:01:09.960
you invite me and set the table for me in front of my enemies

00:01:10.560 --> 00:01:17.520
you greet me like a householder his guest and fill my cup to the brim

00:01:18.400 --> 00:01:21.640
your goodness and love accompany me day after day

00:01:22.400 --> 00:01:24.280
in your house I may stay

00:01:25.040 --> 00:01:25.880
all my life

00:01:26.880 --> 00:01:28.320
I want to say a short prayer

00:01:28.480 --> 00:01:32.000
when you are plagued by worries and fears again and again

00:01:32.720 --> 00:01:35.840
Father thank you so much for the person listening here right now

00:01:36.360 --> 00:01:39.840
and I know that you see our situations Jesus

00:01:40.160 --> 00:01:45.600
you know our hearts and I know that you don't care how we are

00:01:46.240 --> 00:01:47.280
i believe in it

00:01:47.600 --> 00:01:51.120
that you have a solution to our problems

00:01:51.440 --> 00:01:53.960
I believe that you are the solution!

00:01:54.360 --> 00:01:57.520
Jesus you are the answer to our longing

00:01:58.040 --> 00:02:02.640
I know that you have always heard me and also heard me again today

00:02:03.080 --> 00:02:05.920
and I also pray that the person who is listening

00:02:06.320 --> 00:02:10.360
knows that she can speak to you and can trust firmly in it

00:02:10.600 --> 00:02:12.820
that you hear Jesus

00:02:12.821 --> 00:02:15.041
 in Jesus' name Amen
